    correct: 1,
    explanation: 'CARRY_TRUTH.md: «The optimizer\'s +1.08pp is a $100k-scale artifact; at the fundable size that underlies the $100M thesis, today\'s universe cannot support it». Это и есть ценный честный вывод.',
